videos.description: Paschal Chukwu is the beneficiary of some slick passing by Syracuse.
videos.headline: Cuse uses tic-tac-toe passing to set up dunk

videos.description: Frank Howard and Marek Dolezaj drop consecutive 3-pointers to build Syracuse's lead to 13.
videos.headline: Back-to-back 3-pointers forces Pitt timeout

videos.description: Pittsburgh's Terrell Brown gets loose behind Syracuse's 2-3 zone to stuff home a pass and force a timeout.
videos.headline: Alley-oop caps 9-0 Pitt run

videos.description: Trey McGowens thought he had a shot at a 4-point play but the referee called him for a foul.
videos.headline: Pitt crowd furious over call on 3-pointer
